1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:01,010
Here's why.

2
00:00:01,359 --> 00:00:08,691
In the long, long history of humankind, a speaking language, even remotely resembling what we use today,

3
00:00:08,719 --> 00:00:10,691
is a very recent invention.

4
00:00:11,040 --> 00:00:15,169
So recent, you might say, in terms of the great clock of time,

5
00:00:15,199 --> 00:00:18,210
that we developed a language only this morning.

6
00:00:18,480 --> 00:00:26,769
For millions and millions of years, people got by with little more than moans and groans and grunts and growls.

7
00:00:27,680 --> 00:00:35,889
So for millions of years, people communicated with other people by body and facial expressions and sounds, not words.

8
00:00:36,239 --> 00:00:42,370
And we still communicate our attitudes, our feelings toward people and things the same way.

9
00:00:42,719 --> 00:00:51,971
Aside from direct body contact, body movements, facial expressions and sound are the only ways we have to communicate with infants.

10
00:00:52,161 --> 00:00:57,169
And those young ones show an uncanny ability to spot the phony.

11
00:00:57,840 --> 00:01:03,411
Professor Erwin H. Schell, one of America's most respected authorities on leadership,

12
00:01:03,439 --> 00:01:10,210
says, Obviously, there is something more than facilities and competence that makes for accomplishment.

13
00:01:10,560 --> 00:01:15,411
I have come to believe that this linkage factor, this catalyst, if you will,

14
00:01:15,600 --> 00:01:18,850
can be defined in a single word—attitude.

15
00:01:19,120 --> 00:01:26,930
When our attitude is right, our abilities reach a maximum of effectiveness, and good results inevitably follow.

16
00:01:28,000 --> 00:01:30,449
Attitudes do make the difference.

17
00:01:30,719 --> 00:01:33,811
Salesmen with the right attitude beat their quotas.

18
00:01:34,000 --> 00:01:36,691
Students with the right attitude make A's.

19
00:01:36,881 --> 00:01:40,930
Right attitudes pave the way to really happy married life.

20
00:01:41,199 --> 00:01:47,170
Right attitudes make you effective in dealing with people, enable you to develop as a leader.

21
00:01:47,439 --> 00:01:51,170
Right attitudes win for you in every situation.

22
00:01:51,759 --> 00:01:54,050
Grow these three attitudes.

